Privacy Policy for "Mawaslati" App  

Effective Date: 2024-12-12

At "Mawaslati," we prioritize your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data and ensuring its safe and transparent use. This policy explains how we collect, use, and share your information when you use our app.  



 1. Information We Collect  

When you use the "Mawaslati" app, we may collect the following information:  

 A) Personal Information  
- Name: Collected during the registration process.  
- Phone Number: Used for account verification and to facilitate communication with you regarding your bookings.  

 B) Technical Information  
- Device Information: Such as device type, operating system, unique device identifier (Device ID), and other related data.  
- Geolocation Data: We collect your current location using GPS to facilitate booking requests and to help drivers locate you accurately.  

 C) Usage Data  
- Information about how you interact with the app, such as the pages you visit, features you use, and time spent on the app.  



 2. How We Use Your Data  

We use the collected information for the following purposes:  
- Service Delivery: To process bookings, determine your current location, and connect you with available drivers.  
- Service Improvement: To enhance the user experience and analyze app usage.  
- User Communication: To send you push notifications and important updates regarding your bookings.  
- Safety and Security: To protect users from fraud and ensure the security of the platform.  



 3. Data Sharing with Third Parties  

We may share your information with third parties in the following cases:  
- Drivers: Your name and location are shared with drivers to facilitate trip requests.  
- Service Providers: We may work with third-party providers (like analytics or technical support providers) who adhere to this privacy policy.  
- Legal Requirements: If required by law or in response to official government requests, we may disclose your information.  



 4. Data Protection  

We take strong technical and organizational measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. Our protection methods include:  
- Encryption: Data transmitted through the app is encrypted using industry-standard protocols.  
- Access Control: Access to personal information is limited to employees and partners who need it to provide services.  



 5. User Rights  

As a user, you have the following rights regarding your personal information:  
- Access Your Data: Request access to the personal information we hold about you.  
- Edit or Delete Your Data: Request corrections or deletion of your personal information at any time.  
- Opt-Out of Notifications: You can disable push notifications via your device settings.  



 6. Cookies and Tracking Technologies  

We may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to collect information about how you interact with the app. You can modify your device settings to disable cookies, but this may affect the app's functionality.  



 7. Changes to the Privacy Policy  

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. If significant changes are made, we will notify you within the app. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about our privacy practices.  



 8. Contact Us  

If you have any questions about this privacy policy or would like to exercise your rights, please contact us




Thank you for trusting "Mawaslati." We are committed to protecting your data and providing a safe and reliable experience.
